    "updated_at": "2017-02-14T08:22:13Z",
    "body": "This bug is still in the game, for those that want a fix, you can respond to the `resize` event on your window and disable the shadow again.\r\n```js\r\nwin.on('resize', () => {\r\n    win.setHasShadow(false);\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\nHere's an example of before and after resize:\r\n![Before](http://i.imgur.com/dCK3pIB.png)\r\n![After](http://i.imgur.com/SCH6ldu.png)"
